---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About">
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p class="lede" style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.2rem;">
    A short introduction goes here. Replace with your bio.
  </p>

  <p>
    Write a few paragraphs about who you are, what you build, and what you're
    interested in. Markdown formatting (links, emphasis, code) all works inside
    this section if you'd rather author it as a <code>.md</code> file later.
  </p>

  <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/">LinkedIn</a></li>
    <li><a href="mailto:hello@example.com">Email</a></li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
